[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "大変大変大変！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00634",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "騒がしいわね。そんなに繰り返さなくても\n聞こえてるわよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00635",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "昼にアタシたちが投稿した動画……\nなんかすごい拡散されてるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00636",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "本当でありまするか？　どれどれ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00637",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00638",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "何よ。なんなのよ、黙っちゃって。やっと私たちの\n実力に見合った数字になったってことでしょ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00639",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "はあっ！？　１０万再生！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00640",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "いったい、何があったでござるか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00641",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "コメント読めば分かるんじゃない？\nなんて書いてあるのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00642",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ええと……「これが現代に残るニンジャか！」\n「すごい！　どうやってるんだ、これ！？」",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00643",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "やっぱり、忍術が刺さったということでありましょうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00644",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "「鬼門ちゃんかわいい！　目を離さないよ！」\n「動体視力鍛えなきゃ……」",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00645",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "最後のセリフが良かったんじゃない？\n鬼門自体にハマった人もいるみたいよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00646",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "鬼門だけじゃないよ。ヨハナにハマった人もいるみたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00647",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "なんでよ？　あの動画、私何もしてなかったじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00648",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "でも、そんな中でも私の天才さに気付いた人が\nいるってわけね。ほめてあげるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00649",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "「ヨハナちゃん、クールなだけじゃないんだ！」\n「隠しきれないこの無邪気さ、推せます」",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00650",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00651",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ギャップが受けたようでござるなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00652",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "消せ消せ消せ消せ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00653",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "まあまあ、落ち着いて落ち着いて。\nここまで拡散したらもう消せないよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00654",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "それに、いいことじゃない？　新たな魅力が顕現！\nって感じで。この方向を検討してみても……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00655",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "アイドルのヨハナは、クールで天才で歌と踊りが完璧な\n世界一のアイドルなの！　こんなの私じゃないわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00656",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "あっ、ヨハナ！\n……そんなに嫌なのかなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00657",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "きっと、思うところがあるのでございましょう。\n……おや？　このコメント……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00658",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "どうかしたの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00659",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "いや、なんでもないでござる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00660",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]